What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Roll-Your-Own Tobacco Product Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Roll-Your-Own Tobacco Product Market

The roll-your-own tobacco product market size is expected to reach a value of USD 10.48 billion by 2028 and is likely to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 4.30% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Roll-your-own tobacco product market report analyses the growth, which is currently being growing due to strong presence of various well-established players and several small and medium players.

Roll-your-own tobacco is a type of a loose tobacco that the consumer places inside rolling paper and burns. It is a kind of a combustible tobacco product.

The rapid shift in the preference for hand rolled or handmade cigarettes as they are comparatively less expensive compared to factory-made (FM) cigarettes is one of the major factors anticipated to drive the roll-your-own tobacco product market growth rate. Moreover, the handmade cigarettes are usually subject to fewer regulations and less taxation which is also expected to fuel the growth of the roll-your-own tobacco product market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Also the market is largely driven by the high smoking rate. Additionally, the many handmade cigarette smokers believe that roll-your-own tobacco products are less harmful when compared to FM cigarettes which are also expected to highly impact the growth of the roll-your-own tobacco product market. While, the rapid rise in the environmental concerns amongst consumers have obliged vendors to offer innovative and eco-friendly products such as treeless cigarette rolling papers and filter tips which is also amongst the major factors expected to fuel the growth of the roll-your-own tobacco product market in the above mentioned forecast period.

In addition, the high adoption rate of the product amongst the youth in emerging economies are rapid shift in demand is leading in high demand for roll-your-own tobacco products are expected to bring various opportunities that will lead to the growth of the roll-your-own tobacco product market in the above mentioned forecast period.

However, the various restrictions and prohibition imposed on the sale of flavored products in various emerging countries is expected to act as a major limiting factor for roll-your-own tobacco product market, whereas the, various ill-effects associated with the product consumption can challenge the growth of the roll-your-own tobacco product market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

